      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="u-max-content-width u-max-content-width--narrow">
      <div class="l-event-archive__content">
        <h1 class="l-event-archive__title">Arrangementer</h1>
        <div class="l-event-archive__leading">
          Alle kommende og avholdte arrangementer
